Package: openthesaurus-de-text
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: ding
Description: German Text Thesaurus for e.g. ding
 This package contains the German OpenThesaurus (www.openthesaurus.de) thesaurus
 for usage with e.g. ding.

